data.description: Welcome to your new oasis in the heart of Port Orange! This beautifully maintained single-family home is nestled in the sought-after community of Riverwood Plantation, offering an idyllic blend of comfort, convenience, and an abundance of amenities. This spacious 1,597 square-foot residence boasts three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is perfectly updated with custom-made cabinets, quartz countertops, and beautiful glass tile backsplash. Your master suite is truly a retreat, offering an oversized bedroom, walk-in closet, and an expansive master bathroom with split vanities. The woodburning fireplace in the living room creates a perfectly cozy feel while the vaulted ceilings keep the home feeling open and bright. Step outside to the screened-in porch and fenced-in backyard, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. The property also features a generous 2-car garage. The exterior has been freshly painted, making the home feel clean and welcoming. You'll enjoy hassle-free living with included lawn maintenance. The property is situated in the great Port Orange school district, ensuring a top-notch education for your family. Plus, you're just minutes away from the great shopping Port Orange has to offer and the stunning beaches that Florida is renowned for. Riverwood Plantation is a picturesque community characterized by mature landscaping and an array of amenities, including a clubhouse, community pool, playground, tennis, pickleball, racquetball, and basketball courts. For those who love nature and the water, there's a beautiful nature walk that leads to a private fishing dock on Spruce Creek. The community also has a private boat ramp to Spruce Creek exclusively for residents. Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the storage lot for trailers and RVs. Riverwood Plantation is just a short distance to All Children's Park and Neighbors Ice Cream Parlor. This home is not just a place to live, it's a lifestyle. The beautifully maintained interior, spacious rooms, and the allure of living in a thriving community make this a dream come true for anyone looking for the perfect Florida home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful property your own! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm of Riverwood Plantation for yourself.
